templateName: Verification of Merchant(Supporter Package) without Issuer code but with transaction code by Website Admin
emailDescription: Email sent to merchant when website admin verifies merchant with partner package but without issuer code. This email will include the login credentials, login url and the transaction verification code of the merchant. Steps
subject: Registration Successful
emailContent: Dear {merchant},Congratulations! Youre in! It gives us great pleasure to let you know that your Registration with TouristSaver has been successful.  We do have a few quick steps to finalise everything before youre up and running and welcoming TouristSaver Members into your business.  STEP 1: Login CredentialsPlease use the following credentials to login to your Dashboard. We suggest that you copy and paste your username and password when logging in for the first time.Username : {merchant_username}Password : {password}Click here to login to your Dashboard. STEP 2: Once Youre Logged InGo to your Dashboard Menu on left and read the Terms and Conditions STEP 3: Lets Get You Visible and Added to the Piink App PRONTO. To Enable your business to be added to the TouristSaver AppTo do this, we need some info from you:Go to your Dashboard Menu on the left and follow these steps: choose:MY ACCOUNT > PAYMENT METHODS > ADD CARD > COMPLETE YOUR CARD DETAILS > SAVE CARDPlease note: Only you, as a merchant can see your credit card details - this card is used by TouristSaver via Stripe, to debit your 3% monthly Friendship Fee - this fee is only charged on completed transactions with TouristSaver members.  NOTE: Your business will not appear on the TouristSaver App until STEP 3 is completed.  STEP 4: Locating Your Transaction Code. Heres how: MENU > MY ACCOUNT > MY PROFILE You will use this transaction verification code when you make a sale/transact with TouristSaver membersYour transaction verification code{transaction_verification_code} STEP 5: FOR PREMIUM MERCHANTS - Accessing Your Premium CodesHeres how: MENU > PREMIUM CODESAs per your package, you have received {premium_member_codes_count} premium member codes. As a Premium Merchant, you can Register Premium Members and earn a percentage every time they spend their TouristSaver Credits at yours AND other TouristSaver Merchants Businesses. HOT TIP: Explore your entire TouristSaver Dashboard. Click on everything and become familiar with whats available to help you grow your business. Click on the TRAINING tab on the left hand side, these short videos will be your go to when it comes to how the TouristSaver Technology works within your business. You can reach out to us at any time by using the Contact TouristSaver tab on your Menu. We look forward to supporting you as you find your feet & learn the ropes.

emailDescription: This email is sent to the Singapore
subject: TouristSaver Merchant Bonus
emailContent: Dear {merchant_name},   Please accept TouristSavers special thank you, for your patience while our infrastructure was being set up. The great news is that your patience will be rewarded by virtue of the incentives laid out below.  As you can see from the incentive table it is critical that you take advantage of this offer right now to receive the optimal incentive. Each of these Premium memberships you receive, sell for $50 each.    Also remember that you have the option to use a flexible discount structure throughout the day, you can deliver more value to your customers and boost customer footfall and retention. Plus, you'll enjoy increased revenue and an improved reputation. All of this is accessible on your own Merchant dashboard.  Your TouristSaver Merchant Dashboards are designed to add value to your business operations by providing a backend that helps automate accounting tasks, whilst giving you transparent, live, and accurate data.  You should have your TouristSaver Dashboard activation details, which allow you to login and activate your account, if not, make contact today with your sales agent or adminsg@piiink.org to take advantage of this generous BONUS OFFER! These Bonuses are applicable to Merchants whose dashboards were activated prior to 30th June 2023.  Thank you for teaming up with TouristSaver, we look forward to helping you achieve your goals and grow your business together.

Please feel free to reach out to us if you have any questions. Sincerely, TouristSaver

emailDescription: Email informing Singapore merchants that TouristSaver is now live in Singapore- asking them  to complete their dashboard activation if not already done.
subject: TouristSaver Is Live
emailContent: Dear {merchant},Welcome to TouristSaver Live!  A special thank you to you, as a TouristSaver Foundation & Pioneer Merchant for bearing with us as we worked through the process of getting all our infrastructure in place.  As a merchant, you should have had access to your Dashboard for quite some time.  If you have not activated your dashboard, please do so now as you cannot start transacting until this process is completed. As you are in on the ground floor, we dont want you to miss out on this opportunity.  If you need help to activate your merchant dashboard, please contact your Agent or email adminsg@piiink.org and we will get you started. Within your dashboard, on the menu, there is a Training section that offers step by step guidelines and videos to assist you in making the most of TouristSaver.  As you start transacting you will be able to see all your TouristSaver transactions and activity, giving you an insight as to how TouristSaver can help grow your business.  Also, as pioneer and foundation merchants, we're also including a special incentive for you when you activate your dashboard. This is to show our deep appreciation for being patient during our launch phase. Please contact your sales agent for details and to help with your activation. Once again, we truly appreciate your patience and thank you for teaming up with TouristSaver, we look forward to helping you achieve your goals and grow your business together.
